{{Infobox ethnic group|
| group = Khodmooni
| flag = 
| population = ''c. ''100,000 (2004), 200,000 (est. as of 2014)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.everytongue.com/larestani/|title=larestani|publisher=EveryTongue|date=22 March 2014 |accessdate=March 22, 2014}}</ref>
| popplace = [[Southern Iran]], [[Kuwait]], [[Bahrain]], [[UAE]], [[Qatar]]
| langs = [[Achomi language|Achomi]], [[Persian language|Persian]]
| rels = [[Sunni Islam]]
| related = Other [[Iranian peoples]], [[Hola (ethnic group)]]
