'''Det Schubotheske Forlag''' was a Danish [[publishing house]]. It was founded in 1728 by Frantz Christian Mumme.<ref name="Wambergforlag1970">{{cite book|last=Wamberg|first=Niels Birger|title=Digterne og Gyldendal|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IasXAAAAIAAJ|accessdate=13 February 2013|year=1970|publisher=Gyldendal|isbn=978-87-00-45511-5|page=21|language=Danish}}</ref> It was disestablished in 1909. Some of the publications were written in [[Icelandic language|Icelandic]] or [[Old Norse]].
