'''Mid Point''' is a skiway located in the [[East Antarctic Ice Sheet]] at midway between [[Zucchelli Station]] and the inland [[Concordia Station]]. Mid Point Airstrip, being at {{convert|530|km}} from Zucchelli, is a refuelling place for the aircraft on their way to Concordia. The place is equipped with shelters, meteorological equipment, [[fuel bladder]]s and tractors to clean the airstrip. An American researchers team lived at the camp for a time, in 2000, to carry out a project of [[ice drilling]].<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.gdargaud.net/Antarctica/AntarBases.html | title = Mid Point Charlie | website = gdargaud.net | publisher = | accessdate = October 11, 2018}}</ref>
